
Portlets:
--------
- navigation tree
- folder contents
- locale selector (already started)
- images, ads, ...
- flash animations
- event calendar
- RSS box
- Presence box
- CPS3TaskBox
- ...

Portlets to port to Plone:
-------------------------
- content portlet (cf. getContentItems.py)
- language portlet (cf. LinguaPlone)

Portlet management:
------------------
- portlet override

User interface:
---------------
- setting the portlet's visibility range
- direct editing of portlets. (cf. Zope4Media)

Cache:
-----
- invalidation through the event service
- cache cleaning (e.g. when a user log out)

ESI (Edge-Side-Includes):
------------------------
- replacing portlets with <esi> markup

Tests:
------
- cross-platform tests (CMF/CPS/Plone)

Installation:
-------------
- cross-platform installation (CMF/CPS/Plone)
